  • java.lang.Object

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class InternalVoxelizedWorld
extends VoxelizedObject
    This object represents the internal voxelized world. It may has been created manually with specified number and dimensions of voxels, or with a 3D-scan.
    Author:
    Guitard Alan
    See Also:
